
Download the data set from Data folder  (Alternatively you can download the data from this link http://grouplens.org/datasets/movielens/1m/)
It consist of 3 data sets namely

(1) Movies (moviedId,title,genre)
(2) Ratings (userId,movieId,rating,timestamp)
(3) Users (userid,gender,age,occupation,zipcode)

Write the HQL queries to achieve the following scenario:
1.Find top ten mostly viewed movies with their movies Name (Ascending or Descending order)

2. Find top twenty rated movies (Condition: The movie should be rated/viewed by at least 40 users)

3. Find how the genres are ranked by average rating for each profession, and age group. The age groups to be considered are 18-35,36-50 and 50+
Output should have the following columns Occupation,AgeGroup,Genre,Rank